  - m_Id: 555683245187465
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187466
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187467
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187468
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187469
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187470
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187471
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187472
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187473
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187474
    m_Localized: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uB85C \uC678\uBD80\uC5D0 \uB4DC\uB7EC\uB098\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC74C"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187475
    m_Localized: 'Damage: Launches a sword energy wave and deals damage equal to
      <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b> of ATK to the enemy.

      Special Effect
      : The sword energy travels to the end of the map.

      AoE: 3 tiles forward
      on the X-axis.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187476
    m_Localized: "Damage : Swings a scythe widely, dealing damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b>
      of ATK to the enemy. \nSpecial Effect : Enemies hit will have their ATK SPD
      <b><color=#F75D32>reduced by 50%</color></b>\nfor <b><color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color></b>\nAoE
      : 3 tiles forward on the X-axis."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187477
    m_Localized: "Effect : Grants allies a shield equal to <b><color=#F75D32>1000%</color></b>
      of Mensha\u2019s ATK for <b><color=#F75D32>4 seconds</color></b> \nAoE : Same
      row as Mensha."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187478
    m_Localized: "Damage : Deals magic damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>300%</color></b>
      of ATK. \nSpecial Effect : The Skill ATK <b><color=#F75D32>increases by 150%</color></b>against
      the enemies with fire synergy.\nTarget : Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187479
    m_Localized: 'Damage : Summons a flame bean and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>350%</color></b>
      of ATK.

      Special Effect : Leaves residual heat in AoE, dealing <b><color=#F75D32>75%</color></b>
      damage per second for<b><color=#F75D32>2 seconds.</color></b>

      AoE: 3x3
      area centered on the nearest enemy.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187480
    m_Localized: "Damage : Fires a shotgun and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>400%</color></b>
      of Philia\u2019s ATK.\nSpecial Effect : If an enemy is killed by the skill,\nSkill
      Cooldown is reset immediately. \nTarget : Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187481
    m_Localized: "Damage : Deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>850%</color></b>
      of ATK. \nSpecial Effect : Enemy hit is \n <b><color=#F75D32>knocked back</color></b>
      by two tiles. \nTarget : 1 enemy with the highest ATK."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187482
    m_Localized: "Damage : Strikes forcefully and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>250%</color></b>
      of ATK. \nSpecial Effect : Enemies hit are afflicted with <b><color=#F75D32>Silence
      Debuff for 3 seconds.</color></b>\n<color=#77889A><b><color=#F75D32>*</color></b>Silence
      : Skill Usage Disabled, Skill Cooldown Reduction Halted</color>\nTarget : Nearest
      enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187483
    m_Localized: "Damage : Summons flames and deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>450%</color></b>
      of ATK.\nSpecial Effect : If the enemy hit has a shield,\ndestroys the enemy\u2019s
      shield immediately. \nAoE : 3x3 area centered on Rukida."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187484
    m_Localized: 'Effect : Increases the ATK by <b><color=#F75D32>30%</color></b>
      for<b><color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color></b>

      Target : 2 allies with the
      highest ATK.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187485
    m_Localized: "Effect : Recovers all allies\u2019 HP by <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b>
      of Enki\u2019s ATK, and increases the ATK SPD by <b><color=#F75D32>40%</color></b>
      for \n<b><color=#F75D32>2 seconds.</color></b>\nTarget : All allies."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187486
    m_Localized: "Damage : Equal to <color=#F75D32>500%</color> of Tetora\u2019s
      ATK + increased damage proportional to Magic DEF.\nEffect : Swings the greatsword
      and deals damage to 1 enemy, knocking the enemy back by <color=#F75D32>4 tiles.</color>\n
      \nSpecial Effect : If the knocked-back enemy collides with a structure or character,
      the enemy is stunned for <color=#F75D32>1.5 seconds</color> in a 3*3 area\nand
      take additional damage equal to <color=#F75D32>200%</color> of ATK+damage proportional
      to Magic DEF. \n \nAoE : Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187487
    m_Localized: "Damage : Launches a grenade at the enemy and deals damage equal
      to <color=#F75D32>250%</color> of ATK. The grenade detonates after targeting
      the enemy, dealing additional <color=#F75D32>150%</color> damage to the area.
      \nTarget : 3 enemies with the lowest current HP."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187488
    m_Localized: "Damage: Deals damage equal to <color=#F75D32>250%</color> of ATK
      to nearby enemies and knocks them back in a cross-shaped area outward. \nEffect
      : Grants a <color=#F75D32>50%</color> DEF Up Buff to self for <color=#F75D32>4
      seconds.</color> \nBonus Effect : Increases Phys DEF by additional <color=#F75D32>25%</color>
      for each Wind Synergy unit deployed.\n(Max: 3 units) \n \nAoE : Cross-shaped
      area centered on self."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187489
    m_Localized: "Effect : Seals the enemy in a coffin for <color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color>
      Sealed enemy can still be targeted, but their Skill Cooldown will not progress.
      \nTarget : Enemy with the highest ATK."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187490
    m_Localized: "Damage : Deals damage equal to <color=#F75D32>500%</color> of Adria\u2019s
      ATK, and the damage increases proportional to<color=#F75D32>Phys DEF</color>.\nBonus
      Effect : Enemies within the AoE are stunned for <color=#F75D32>1 second.</color>\nAoE
      : Self-Centered."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187491
    m_Localized: "Effect : Summons a bear for {0} seconds. Upon summoning, deals
      damage equal to {1}% of Pippin\u2019s ATK in a 3*3 area centered on the bear.
      The summoned bear casts a taunt that lasts for {0} seconds in 3*3 area. \nBear
      Stats : 200% of Pippin\u2019s HP, 70% of Pippin\u2019s ATK, all other stats
      are identical to Pippin. \nTarget : Enemies around the target Pippin is currently
      attacking."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187492
    m_Localized: "AoE : 1 tile, 3 tiles, 5 tiles, 7 tiles forward. \nEffect : Unleashes
      multiple firearms over a wide area, striking <color=#F75D32>10 times</color>
      over <color=#F75D32>3 seconds</color>, with different damage based on the AoE
      range.\nDamage : \n-1 and 3 tiles forward: damage equal to <color=#F75D32>900%</color>
      of ATK per strike\n-5 tiles forward: damage equal to <color=#F75D32>700%</color>
      of ATK per strike\n-7 tiles forward: damage equal to<color=#F75D32>500%</color>
      of ATK per strike."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187493
    m_Localized: "Damage : Throws a boomerang at the enemy and deals damage equal
      to <color=#F75D32>300%</color> of ATK. \nIf there is another enemy near the
      target hit, the boomerang bounces to that enemy.\nEach time boomerang bounces,
      its damage reduces by <color=#F75D32>50%.</color>\nThe boomerang can hit up
      to <color=#F75D32>5 enemies.</color>\nBonus Effect : ATK SPD increases by <color=#F75D32>10%</color>
      for 2 seconds per enemy hit. \nTarget: Nearest enemy."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187494
    m_Localized: 'Effect : Drops a vial, reducing healing effects of enemies within
      range by <color=#F75D32>60%</color>

      and Phys DEF by <color=#F75D32>80%</color>
      for <color=#F75D32>3 seconds.</color>

      Target : 3*3 area around the enemy
      with the highest Phys DEF and Magic DEF.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187495
    m_Localized: Explosion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187496
    m_Localized: Freezing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187497
    m_Localized: Airborne
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187498
    m_Localized: Life Heal
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187499
    m_Localized: Teleport
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187500
    m_Localized: Curse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187501
    m_Localized: "Deals damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>500%</color></b> of allies\u2019
      average ATK to enemies within the area."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187502
    m_Localized: Freezes enemies within a cross-shaped area for 3 seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187503
    m_Localized: Airbornes 1 selected enemy for 3 seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187504
    m_Localized: "Restores the HP of allies within the area by 700% of the highest
      ally\u2019s ATK."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187505
    m_Localized: Randomly swaps the positions of allies, enemies, and terrain features
      on the battlefield.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187506
    m_Localized: Reduces ATK of enemies within a 3*3 area by 50% for 5 seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187507
    m_Localized: Guardian
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187508
    m_Localized: <color=#F75D32>High Magic DEF</color>, reducing damage from <color=#F75D32>Mages</color>,
      but powerless against <color=#0047AB>Rangers</color> with physical attacks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187509
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187510
    m_Localized: Tank
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187511
    m_Localized: High <color=#F75D32>Phys DEF</color>, effectively blocks attacks
      of Guardians and <color=#F75D32>Rangers</color>, but powerless agaist <color=#0047AB>Mages</color>
      who use magic attacks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187512
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187513
    m_Localized: Mage
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187514
    m_Localized: Uses <color=#F75D32>magic attacks</color>, effectively hitting<color=#F75D32>Tanks</color>,
      but powerless agaist <color=#0047AB>Guardians</color> with high magic defense.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187515
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187516
    m_Localized: Ranger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187517
    m_Localized: <color=#F75D32>Longest range</color> and <color=#F75D32>High ATK</color>,
      effectively hitting <color=#F75D32>Guardians</color>, but powerless against
      <color=#0047AB>Tanks</color> with high physical defense.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187518
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187519
    m_Localized: Assassin
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187520
    m_Localized: "<color=#F75D32>High ATK SPD</color> and <color=#F75D32>MOV SPD</color>,
      \nwith a short <color=#F75D32>Skill Cooldown.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187521
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187522
    m_Localized: Supporter
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187523
    m_Localized: Specialized in <color=#F75D32>healing, buffing, and debuffing</color>,
      this position focuses on strengthening allies or weakening enemies. Supporters
      have <color=#0047AB>low</color> base ATK and HP.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187524
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187525
    m_Localized: Fire
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187526
    m_Localized: Applies <color=#F75D32>additional damage </color> to the enemies
      when the character attacks
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187527
    m_Localized: '{0}units : Damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> of
      ATK'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187528
    m_Localized: Earth
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187529
    m_Localized: "Increases the character\u2019s <color=#F75D32>Phys DEF.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187530
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> increase of Phys
      DEF'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187531
    m_Localized: Water
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187532
    m_Localized: Generates a <color=#F75D32>shield</color> for the entire team equal
      to the team's average attack power for <color=#F75D32>10 seconds</color>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187533
    m_Localized: '{0}units : A shield equal to <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b>
      of ATK'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187534
    m_Localized: Light
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187535
    m_Localized: Grants a character <color=#F75D32>immunity to all status effects</color>
      for a certain period of time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187536
    m_Localized: '{0}units : Immune for <b><color=#F75D32>{1}seconds</color></b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187537
    m_Localized: Darkness
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187538
    m_Localized: "Reduces the enemy\u2019s <color=#F75D32>Skill Cooldown Reduction
      Speed.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187539
    m_Localized: '{0}units : Reduction by <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187540
    m_Localized: Wind
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 555683245187541
    m_Localized: "Boosts the character\u2019s <color=#F75D32>ATK SPD.</color>"
